values:
things always seem to move too fast with me
but sure enough it heals slow



I'll be fine I'll be fine I'll be fine

Come in, come in, Come into my world I've got to show Show show you. Come into my bed I've got to know know know you. I have dreams of orca whales and owls, But I wake up in fear. You will never be my You will never be my fool. Will never be my fool. Floaters in my eyes,Wake up in an hotel room. Cigarettes and lies. I am a child, it's too soon.

Lying there next to you I had no control. No control of my thoughts, my feelings, my laughter that you caught me in. I pulled you closer and you smiled at me and asked me what I was so happy about. I didn't tell you, but I wanted to tell you. You are what makes me happy. The happiest I've felt in so long. So, so long. Instead I avoided the question, saying I didn't know what it was I just felt happy. I just felt really good being there. With you. Lying next to you. Hearing you breathe and watching your mouth move, talk about random football players I didn't know of and rest on your chest as it sank up and down. I heard I was cute because of this, which made my insides twirl even more. I feel like a little girl on her birthday, with balloons and presents and ice cream cake and so much ahead of her. Like I have so much to look forward to in such a little amount of time and I'm overwhelmed with happiness. I'm overwhelmed with you and I can't get enough of it. Keep em coming baby, because I can't get enough of you.

Today started on a bad note, but ended amazingly.
I love dinner and board games and crisp weather and your laugh.


"stop tickling me it sucks!"



Grey's Anatomy is going crazy. Don't you agree!
I can't stop watching old episodes online!!
aaahhsdfl;,msldfkwhat to do with myself

time you've got me tired
I need water





I love the look in your eyes when you laugh and I don't let you talk anymore because I won't stop kissing you.
I don't think I've been this happy in a long time. Too long actually. It feels good and I thank you for it.


This is the way things should be. I don't like thinking about it but I'm growing up. I love my friends, I don't deserve them.
Really. I'm selfish.


The sky was so beautiful tonight! I wish I could bottle it up and keep it on my dresser. I wanted to show everyone.
We won semi-states. It was an hour 1/2 away, but worth it. Now we play for the title of best soccer team in Maryland? woah!



Can someone find my Michelle for me? I've lost her.

Today's my first day! Aren't you excited?


I've been thinking lately. Which I know is bad for me. Sometimes I think I want things that I don't need. Like a boyfriend for instance. I catch myself misssing steve, but really I know I only miss the void of what steve and I had. I'vebeen looking for someone to replace that void and I thought I found someone. But he is never there when I need him, only when he needs me.

I can't say I don't play along with him though, I obviously lead him on to thinking that I want what he does. The truth is I want so much more than only physicality.




Tonight is the last night of summer! I'm sad its over but at the same time I'm grateful for it, and excited for new beginnings. Can you believe that this time next year I'll be going to college? I don't want to grow up now that its actually happening. I want to stay young and have my mom go grocery shopping for me and do my laundry and be the only one who knows how much peanut butter to put on my sandwiches. I dont want to wake up to an empty house just to work all day then come home to a big bed for only me. 


Live the dream, because you have to wake up sometime.

we made a fort last night. I basically did all of the work. which makes me really sad. I went to the driving meeting last night at school and it just reminded me of lunch which reminds me I have to wake up early next week to go back. and its my last year in high school. THE LAST ONE. I can't believe that I've waited so long to grow up and now that its finally happening I don't want to anymore. Its a strange feeling, getting older and beginning to realize that I wont be seeing the same people I have seen the past 3 years anymore. The friends I know could turn into people I don't. I'm feeling sentimental. I am going to enjoy this year regardless, its only the beginning.

<center>it was the end of summer and we walked home together, but slept alone. you left me like there was a good reason to leave, but all i could get out of you were the excuses i somehow believed. that was a year ago.

i hope you know you're the reason i stopped asking questions and kept so quiet. you're the reason that i'm no longer right. you're the reason i'm not the way you always wanted me to be. a part of me wishes you'd ask if this was about you. i hate you.

i've gotten rid of your number, but who am i kidding; its still in memory.

I really like the song Lips of an Angel awwwwwww school in t minus soon! Visited Taco bell again tonight, duh then went to play in the bubbles at the village center after work with k and m I also need a new job and a polaroid camera let me know if youre selling one:)

I swear my life consists of taco bell and spending money. Michelle, Kristen and I are going to Tampa in October to visit a college. I want to see Timothy :) and go to Busch Gardens FIELD hockey tryouts. are on. tuesday (trigger to head)
today bored me!! Tomorrow I'm going to get a physical, then buy a new stick for FH. I really just don't want summer to end. PLEASE. PS- there aint jack to do in colombibiaiaaaa

and I am making ziti. mm I saw the ricky bobby movie tonight with mich and then went to taco B excellente I fought the war but the war won. I fought the war but the war won. I fought the war but the war won't stop for the love of god. I fought the war but the war won. I miss you I can't mess this up. Not this time, no.

woke up around 12 by accident...I wanted to go running at 830 (psh yeah right) but I just suck. got ready and michelle kristen and I went to ruby's to celebrate dan's 40th birthday. actually hes 24 but hes still old. we werent up for a movie so we went home,. and I ended up going back out to dinner at tgifridays with ryan david alex bray and stevie. we told them it was ryan's birthday so we got a free ice cream.. and since I wasnt hungry stevie and I just split a slice of cinnabon cheesecake which wasnt that good. thenn randomly we went to a driving range and hit golf balls (that I'm pretty good at I might add) but really I just played field hockey with a golf club.

ohwell I'm a G they'll let me play

goiodngihtt!!

its been a reeeeeeeeeaaally long time since I've even thought about LJ but this is cool I guess today is my mom's birthday, and I got home from ocean city today. kristen michelle kelley and i stayed at her aunts place in fenwick which is literally 5 minutes from ocean city. it was cool because we had no parents or supervision or anything. it kind of felt like they were my roommates, and made me think about college and frightened me even more. its funny, because when I was young I always wanted to be old. and now that I'm growing up I wish I could still play with my barbies or not worry about how I look in a bikini and just build sandcastles. overall, ocean city was amazing. the beach was beautiful, and we stopped by bethany for a night. ha it seemed like a private school there, everyone knew each other and popped their collars. we met a lot of drunk people and funny guys on the bus. ate tons of subway and stalked surfers. right on! howard county is whack and I dont want school to start................ seriously beach pictures kristen^^ ^^hothothot surfer boys phillip(sitting) and rob now I just really want to sleep in my own, air conditioned bed in the room my mom decided to clean out while I was away. yeahhhhhhhhhhhh john casey HA

i'm so sick of hearing about things that i wish would just be dropped..and i wish people would just move on and accept the way things are now. whats done is done and if i dont want to go back to how things used to be, then thats my choice. "I miss you" and "things arent the same". seriously, shut the fuck up. its your own fault things are this way so suck it up and get used to it.. you should be by now. why am i going to waste so much time and effort into something when i know its just going to be screwed up in the end? i can learn to be happy without you. i have learned it. its not difficult when youre such a different person than how you used to be and i'm sick of hearing the same meaningless attempts to get me back over and over. the only thing you want out of me is knowing you can have me...and i'm not giving you that advantage again.


take your bullshit and feed it to some other gullible girl, because i'm not one of them anymore.

Nothing is more amazing. Nothing is more amazing.. Nothing is more amazing. You are everything. You are mine. Nothing has felt this good. I am happier now than I have ever been. Keep it real. Lets keep it real baby. Mmmmmm.....


I am in love.
